tell every one of your male clients</b></i></font>

479
00:19:53,150 --> 00:19:55,118
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>when you meet them
that you're going to rob them,</b></i></font>

480
00:19:55,528 --> 00:19:59,374
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and then your cushy job making $1
million per sucker is going away...</b></i></font>

481
00:19:59,448 --> 00:20:00,448
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Or?</b></i></font>

482
00:20:00,491 --> 00:20:02,664
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Or you're going
to tell me about every time</b></i></font>

483
00:20:02,743 --> 00:20:04,711
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you've done this
for James Palmer.</b></i></font>

484
00:20:04,787 --> 00:20:06,755
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you're never going to hear
from either one of us again.</b></i></font>

485
00:20:06,997 --> 00:20:08,340
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't do that.</b></i></font>

486
00:20:08,416 --> 00:20:10,589
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>My job requires
a reputation for discretion.</b></i></font>

487
00:20:10,668 --> 00:20:11,669
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're going to do
what we want,</b></i></font>

488
00:20:11,752 --> 00:20:15,006
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>or you're going to find out how much
your reputation protects you in prison.</b></i></font>

489
00:20:16,507 --> 00:20:19,886
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, I get it. You're not
worried about Palmer knowing.</b></i></font>

490
00:20:20,469 --> 00:20:22,972
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're worried
about word spreading.</b></i></font>

491
00:20:23,347 --> 00:20:25,566
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Trust me,
he'll never tell a soul</b></i></font>

492
00:20:25,641 --> 00:20:27,643
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and your business
will stay intact.</b></i></font>

493
00:20:28,144 --> 00:20:29,566
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How can you be sure?</b></i></font>

494
00:20:30,271 --> 00:20:33,741
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The same way I'm sure
that you don't have a choice.</b></i></font>

495
00:20:33,816 --> 00:20:36,114
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The question is, are you
going to go against him</b></i></font>

496
00:20:36,193 --> 00:20:37,866
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>or are you going
to go against me?</b></i></font>

497
00:20:47,288 --> 00:20:48,540
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Okay, I'm in.</b></i></font>

498
00:20:48,956 --> 00:20:50,333
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Just like that?
Just like that.</b></i></font>

499
00:20:50,416 --> 00:20:51,463
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This thing
is damn impressive.</b></i></font>

500
00:20:51,542 --> 00:20:52,589
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But before
we move forward,</b></i></font>

501
00:20:52,668 --> 00:20:54,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need to make sure
you're good with one thing.</b></i></font>

502
00:20:54,503 --> 00:20:55,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's that?</b></i></font>

503
00:20:56,005 --> 00:20:57,848
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want 90% ownership.</b></i></font>

504
00:20:58,340 --> 00:20:59,842
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>90%?</b></i></font>

505
00:21:00,342 --> 00:21:01,889
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are you out of your mind?
No, I'm not.</b></i></font>

506
00:21:01,969 --> 00:21:04,597
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm not in the venture capital
business. I invest in the stock market.</b></i></font>

507
00:21:04,680 --> 00:21:07,149
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which means I'd be using
my own money on this.</b></i></font>

508
00:21:07,224 --> 00:21:08,396
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Money that you'd
earn back in spades.</b></i></font>

509
00:21:08,476 --> 00:21:09,443
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I hope it turns out
that way.</b></i></font>

510
00:21:09,518 --> 00:21:12,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But this thing has a lot of risk
and I'd be taking all of it.</b></i></font>

511
00:21:12,855 --> 00:21:14,448
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then maybe you should
take none of it.</b></i></font>

512
00:21:14,523 --> 00:21:15,775
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna.</b></i></font>

513
00:21:15,858 --> 00:21:16,898
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>As good as
this product is,</b></i></font>

514
00:21:16,942 --> 00:21:18,910
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm telling you as one
business person to another,</b></i></font>

515
00:21:18,986 --> 00:21:20,613
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you have no credibility
to do this.</b></i></font>

516
00:21:20,696 --> 00:21:23,245
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Believe me, these are the best
terms you're going to get.</b></i></font>

517
00:21:23,324 --> 00:21:26,373
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, you see, that's
where you're wrong, Stu.</b></i></font>

518
00:21:26,827 --> 00:21:29,125
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because like I
told you once before,</b></i></font>

519
00:21:29,205 --> 00:21:33,711
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm Donna, this is awesome,
and I can do better.</b></i></font>

520
00:21:36,462 --> 00:21:38,305
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, I hope
you prove me wrong.</b></i></font>

521
00:21:38,380 --> 00:21:40,803
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But in the meantime, I won't
be used as a stalking horse.</b></i></font>

522
00:21:40,883 --> 00:21:43,483
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which means if you walk away now,
you can't come back to me later.</b></i></font>

523
00:21:43,803 --> 00:21:45,430
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, you don't have to
worry about that, Stu.</b></i></font>

524
00:21:45,513 --> 00:21:47,481
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because once I
walk out that door,</b></i></font>

525
00:21:47,556 --> 00:21:49,433
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I promise you
I'm not coming back.</b></i></font>

526
00:21:54,814 --> 00:21:55,906
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I can't believe you.</b></i></font>

527
00:21:55,981 --> 00:21:57,324
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Listen, Mike, before
you say anything...</b></i></font>

528
00:21:57,399 --> 00:21:58,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know you didn't give a
shit about those miners,</b></i></font>

529
00:21:58,901 --> 00:21:59,993
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but the least
you could have done</b></i></font>

530
00:22:00,069 --> 00:22:01,662
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>was stuck around long enough
to give me some leverage.</b></i></font>

531
00:22:01,737 --> 00:22:03,034
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We had no choice.</b></i></font>

532
00:22:03,113 --> 00:22:04,990
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Palmer pressured
10 of our top clients</b></i></font>

533
00:22:05,074 --> 00:22:06,747
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>to drop us
unless we pulled out.</b></i></font>

534
00:22:06,826 --> 00:22:07,866
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, it's either
them or me.</b></i></font>

535
00:22:07,910 --> 00:22:09,753
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Unless you can replace
$30 million in billings,</b></i></font>

536
00:22:09,829 --> 00:22:10,955
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you're damn right it is.</b></i></font>

537
00:22:11,038 --> 00:22:13,666
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey, without you backing
me, those miners are screwed</b></i></font>

538
00:22:13,749 --> 00:22:15,469
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and there is nothing
that I can do about it.</b></i></font>

539
00:22:15,501 --> 00:22:17,720
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's something you can do about
it, you just don't want to do it.</b></i></font>

540
00:22:18,045 --> 00:22:19,012
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're talking
about that woman.</b></i></font>

541
00:22:19,088 --> 00:22:20,840
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You want leverage on Palmer,
she's the one who's got it.</b></i></font>

542
00:22:20,923 --> 00:22:22,049
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Harvey,
we've been over this.</b></i></font>

543
00:22:22,132 --> 00:22:23,258
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not going
to use that woman.</b></i></font>

544
00:22:23,342 --> 00:22:25,185
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And what if I told you
we already did?</b></i></font>

545
00:22:26,303 --> 00:22:27,395
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?
Mike...</b></i></font>

546
00:22:27,638 --> 00:22:29,356
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We not only found her,</b></i></font>

547
00:22:29,431 --> 00:22:32,310
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>we got enough to force that
bastard into a settlement.</b></i></font>

548
00:22:32,393 --> 00:22:34,691
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The question is,
are you willing to use it?</b></i></font>

549
00:22:34,770 --> 00:22:36,067
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean, "we"?</b></i></font>

550
00:22:36,438 --> 00:22:38,281
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike. No, no. You
just said "we."</b></i></font>

551
00:22:39,525 --> 00:22:41,027
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Who the hell is "we"?</b></i></font>

552
00:22:41,193 --> 00:22:42,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel.</b></i></font>

553
00:22:43,112 --> 00:22:44,329
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Me and Rachel.</b></i></font>

554
00:22:46,323 --> 00:22:47,916
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You dragged Rachel
into this.</b></i></font>

555
00:22:48,325 --> 00:22:49,702
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I didn't drag her
into anything.</b></i></font>

556
00:22:49,785 --> 00:22:53,289
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I went to her for permission
because I knew how you felt,</b></i></font>

557
00:22:53,372 --> 00:22:55,795
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and she jumped at the chance
since you're too stupid to.</b></i></font>

558
00:22:55,875 --> 00:22:56,876
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You had no right.</b></i></font>

559
00:22:56,959 --> 00:22:57,960
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike, listen to me.</b></i></font>

560
00:22:58,043 --> 00:22:59,795
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You had no right!</b></i></font>

561
00:23:04,258 --> 00:23:05,760
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Night, Johnny.</b></i></font>

562
00:23:08,804 --> 00:23:10,056
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Benjamin?</b></i></font>

563
00:23:10,306 --> 00:23:11,478
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Donna.</b></i></font>

564
00:23:11,974 --> 00:23:13,976
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Uh, I hope you don't think it's
weird that I came to your place.</b></i></font>

565
00:23:14,059 --> 00:23:16,232
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, I find it a little weird
that you know where I live.</b></i></font>

566
00:23:16,312 --> 00:23:18,406
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I work in IT,
I know where everyone lives.</b></i></font>

567
00:23:18,480 --> 00:23:19,902
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But that's not what
I came here to talk about.</b></i></font>

568
00:23:19,982 --> 00:23:21,199
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What did you
come here for?</b></i></font>

569
00:23:21,525 --> 00:23:22,993
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm freaking out
about tomorrow.</b></i></font>

570
00:23:23,068 --> 00:23:24,320
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I mean,
what if we're not ready?</b></i></font>

571
00:23:24,612 --> 00:23:26,410
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Relax, Benjamin,
it's going to be fine.</b></i></font>

572
00:23:26,488 --> 00:23:27,831
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How can you know that?</b></i></font>

573
00:23:27,907 --> 00:23:29,500
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I already
did a practice run.</b></i></font>

574
00:23:29,950 --> 00:23:31,076
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
talking about?</b></i></font>

575
00:23:31,160 --> 00:23:32,582
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's a guy I know
who I thought might invest,</b></i></font>

576
00:23:32,661 --> 00:23:33,913
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but he's not really
in this business.</b></i></font>

577
00:23:33,996 --> 00:23:36,419
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, I brought The Donna over to
him and I gave him our pitch.</b></i></font>

578
00:23:36,498 --> 00:23:38,296
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And it went okay?
It went more than okay.</b></i></font>

579
00:23:38,500 --> 00:23:39,717
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>He made us an offer.</b></i></font>

580
00:23:39,793 --> 00:23:42,637
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then what in God's name do we need to
put ourselves through this torture for?</b></i></font>

581
00:23:42,713 --> 00:23:43,805
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I turned him down.</b></i></font>

582
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:47,184
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Wait. Sorry, what?
Donna, this is our dream.</b></i></font>

583
00:23:47,259 --> 00:23:48,852
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know that, Benjamin.</b></i></font>

584
00:23:48,928 --> 00:23:50,475
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But he wanted
to own 90% of it.</b></i></font>

585
00:23:50,554 --> 00:23:53,103
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm not willing to
give up 90% of our dream.</b></i></font>

586
00:23:53,682 --> 00:23:54,683
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Now, go home
and get some sleep.</b></i></font>

587
00:23:54,767 --> 00:23:56,064
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because we've got our
first meeting tomorrow.</b></i></font>

588
00:23:56,143 --> 00:23:58,191
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And you and I are going
to kick some serious ass.</b></i></font>

589
00:24:11,200 --> 00:24:12,452
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>When were you
going to tell me?</b></i></font>

590
00:24:13,077 --> 00:24:15,705
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Mike... Were you ever
going to goddamn tell me?</b></i></font>

591
00:24:15,829 --> 00:24:17,456
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Don't speak to me like that.
You went behind my back</b></i></font>

592
00:24:17,539 --> 00:24:19,086
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>When you knew
how I felt about this.</b></i></font>

593
00:24:19,166 --> 00:24:23,512
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, I went behind your back because
I knew how you felt about it.</b></i></font>

594
00:24:23,587 --> 00:24:24,884
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Is that supposed
to make it okay?</b></i></font>

595
00:24:24,964 --> 00:24:27,934
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, look, I was the one that didn't
want to let things get too risky.</b></i></font>

596
00:24:28,008 --> 00:24:30,807
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But when Harvey laid it out for
me, I decided that it wasn't.</b></i></font>

597
00:24:30,886 --> 00:24:32,684
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then why didn't you
come to me first?</b></i></font>

598
00:24:32,763 --> 00:24:34,003
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because you're the one
that says</b></i></font>

599
00:24:34,056 --> 00:24:36,058
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>forgiveness is easier
to ask for than permission.</b></i></font>

600
00:24:36,141 --> 00:24:37,358
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's a bullshit reason.</b></i></font>

601
00:24:37,685 --> 00:24:41,440
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then how about focusing on the
fact that I did it for you?</b></i></font>

602
00:24:42,147 --> 00:24:43,649
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel.
Mike,</b></i></font>

603
00:24:43,732 --> 00:24:47,953
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>this morning, when you told me it
was over, the look on your face...</b></i></font>

604
00:24:49,238 --> 00:24:51,286
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't want you to have that
look for the rest of your life.</b></i></font>

605
00:24:51,365 --> 00:24:52,708
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, I was upset.
It had just happened.</b></i></font>

606
00:24:52,783 --> 00:24:55,252
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, Mike. That's just it.
It hadn't.</b></i></font>

607
00:24:55,786 --> 00:24:57,504
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You've been living
with this for so long.</b></i></font>

608
00:24:57,579 --> 00:24:59,832
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's why you gave Harvey
the go-ahead to begin with.</b></i></font>

609
00:24:59,915 --> 00:25:02,134
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I did that because
I had to watch Oliver fail</b></i></font>

610
00:25:02,209 --> 00:25:04,553
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and there was nothing
I could do about it.</b></i></font>

611
00:25:04,878 --> 00:25:06,471
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if it wasn't Oliver,</b></i></font>

612
00:25:06,547 --> 00:25:10,017
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>it was going to be someone
else or something else.</b></i></font>

613
00:25:10,092 --> 00:25:13,687
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There's always going to be some
reminder that you weren't a lawyer.</b></i></font>

614
00:25:15,055 --> 00:25:17,183
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And it would eat away at you because
it's what you're meant to be.</b></i></font>

615
00:25:17,266 --> 00:25:18,706
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You shouldn't have done
what you did.</b></i></font>

616
00:25:18,767 --> 00:25:21,270
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know you're mad at me
for going behind your back.</b></i></font>

617
00:25:22,771 --> 00:25:24,193
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I'm not
going to apologize.</b></i></font>

618
00:25:24,440 --> 00:25:26,067
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I don't want to
spend the rest of my life</b></i></font>

619
00:25:26,150 --> 00:25:27,902
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>with a man who gave
up on his dreams.</b></i></font>

620
00:25:27,985 --> 00:25:30,704
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I know that you don't
want to be that man either.</b></i></font>

621
00:25:41,290 --> 00:25:42,291
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis?</b></i></font>

622
00:25:42,750 --> 00:25:44,218
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you doing
in here?</b></i></font>

623
00:25:44,293 --> 00:25:45,653
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Rachel, can I
talk to you a second?</b></i></font>

624
00:25:45,878 --> 00:25:47,221
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course.</b></i></font>

625
00:25:47,504 --> 00:25:50,303
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I heard Mike had a problem
involving that woman.</b></i></font>

626
00:25:51,300 --> 00:25:52,722
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Yes, he did.</b></i></font>

627
00:25:52,801 --> 00:25:54,895
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We actually got into a fight
about it last night.</b></i></font>

628
00:25:55,888 --> 00:25:57,606
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What's he going to do?
I don't know.</b></i></font>

629
00:25:57,681 --> 00:26:00,901
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But thank you for doing whatever
you did to find her, anyway.</b></i></font>

630
00:26:00,976 --> 00:26:02,319
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course.</b></i></font>

631
00:26:04,646 --> 00:26:05,647
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So.</b></i></font>

632
00:26:06,023 --> 00:26:07,063
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you doing
in here?</b></i></font>

633
00:26:07,107 --> 00:26:08,484
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Do you ever wish
you hadn't found out?</b></i></font>

634
00:26:08,567 --> 00:26:09,568
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

635
00:26:09,651 --> 00:26:12,029
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Do you ever wish you'd never
known about Mike's secret?</b></i></font>

636
00:26:12,112 --> 00:26:15,082
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Or, for that matter,
never even met him?</b></i></font>

637
00:26:16,742 --> 00:26:18,665
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis,
