<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you care about
that weasel's future for?</b></i></font>

796
00:32:57,559 --> 00:32:58,811
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>That's between me and him.</b></i></font>

797
00:32:59,102 --> 00:33:00,194
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh...</b></i></font>

798
00:33:00,270 --> 00:33:01,897
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>One other thing?</b></i></font>

799
00:33:01,980 --> 00:33:03,823
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This really is
a take it or leave it offer.</b></i></font>

800
00:33:04,316 --> 00:33:06,284
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It expires in 15 seconds.</b></i></font>

801
00:33:06,359 --> 00:33:07,531
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And once it's signed,</b></i></font>

802
00:33:07,611 --> 00:33:09,534
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I never want to hear about
your shitty little company</b></i></font>

803
00:33:09,613 --> 00:33:11,707
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>doing something
like this ever again.</b></i></font>

804
00:33:19,581 --> 00:33:20,798
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>There you are.</b></i></font>

805
00:33:20,874 --> 00:33:22,672
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Where have you been
since that meeting?</b></i></font>

806
00:33:23,460 --> 00:33:24,632
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've been doing
some thinking.</b></i></font>

807
00:33:24,711 --> 00:33:28,090
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I've been wondering if my
partner sold me out all day.</b></i></font>

808
00:33:29,799 --> 00:33:30,891
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, I hate to break it
to you, Benjamin,</b></i></font>

809
00:33:30,967 --> 00:33:33,345
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but that's actually the
opposite of what happened.</b></i></font>

810
00:33:33,428 --> 00:33:35,772
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean?
I mean...</b></i></font>

811
00:33:36,139 --> 00:33:37,607
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>They don't want
to make us an offer.</b></i></font>

812
00:33:38,600 --> 00:33:41,149
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>In fact, they don't want
anything to do with The Donna.</b></i></font>

813
00:33:42,312 --> 00:33:43,734
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's my fault,
isn't it?</b></i></font>

814
00:33:43,855 --> 00:33:45,573
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Benjamin... You don't have
to protect my feelings.</b></i></font>

815
00:33:45,649 --> 00:33:49,654
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>A chain is only as strong as its weakest
link, and I know that's what I am.</b></i></font>

816
00:33:49,736 --> 00:33:50,737
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, you're not.</b></i></font>

817
00:33:51,780 --> 00:33:53,453
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Turns out, I am.</b></i></font>

818
00:33:55,116 --> 00:33:56,584
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Listen to me.</b></i></font>

819
00:33:56,993 --> 00:33:59,917
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You have designed
an incredible product,</b></i></font>

820
00:33:59,996 --> 00:34:01,623
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and I don't want
to hold you back.</b></i></font>

821
00:34:02,123 --> 00:34:03,375
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Which is why,
as of right now,</b></i></font>

822
00:34:03,458 --> 00:34:05,256
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I am dissolving
our partnership</b></i></font>

823
00:34:05,335 --> 00:34:07,258
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>so you can take it out
on your own.</b></i></font>

824
00:34:10,799 --> 00:34:12,676
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Where the hell
do you think you're going?</b></i></font>

825
00:34:13,969 --> 00:34:14,969
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We're partners.</b></i></font>

826
00:34:15,011 --> 00:34:17,560
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'd rather throw The Donna into the
ocean than move forward without you.</b></i></font>

827
00:34:17,639 --> 00:34:19,232
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Benjamin, please,
don't be a martyr.</b></i></font>

828
00:34:19,307 --> 00:34:21,184
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not being a martyr.</b></i></font>

829
00:34:21,268 --> 00:34:23,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm being a partner.</b></i></font>

830
00:34:23,478 --> 00:34:26,106
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We're in this together
or not at all.</b></i></font>

831
00:34:26,690 --> 00:34:28,363
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>So, it's up to you.</b></i></font>

832
00:34:28,441 --> 00:34:29,909
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are we going to give up
on our dream?</b></i></font>

833
00:34:30,944 --> 00:34:33,322
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Or live to fight
another day?</b></i></font>

834
00:34:36,449 --> 00:34:38,417
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Live to fight, Benjamin.</b></i></font>

835
00:34:40,245 --> 00:34:41,747
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Live to fight.</b></i></font>

836
00:34:50,505 --> 00:34:51,677
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Again?</b></i></font>

837
00:34:52,465 --> 00:34:54,308
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What the hell is it
this time?</b></i></font>

838
00:34:54,384 --> 00:34:56,386
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The same thing
as it was last time.</b></i></font>

839
00:34:56,469 --> 00:34:58,392
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I need you to get
that hearing back for me.</b></i></font>

840
00:34:58,471 --> 00:35:00,690
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Are you kidding me? You know how
much trouble it was the first time?</b></i></font>

841
00:35:00,765 --> 00:35:03,609
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I don't care how much trouble it was.
You're going to do it again.</b></i></font>

842
00:35:03,685 --> 00:35:05,153
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Unless, of course, you don't
want the original terms</b></i></font>

843
00:35:05,228 --> 00:35:06,855
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>of your deal
with Palmer upheld.</b></i></font>

844
00:35:07,647 --> 00:35:08,899
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
talking about?</b></i></font>

845
00:35:08,982 --> 00:35:10,609
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>We had him guarantee
to pay you what he promised</b></i></font>

846
00:35:10,692 --> 00:35:13,286
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and to hire you over there
at the end of the quarter.</b></i></font>

847
00:35:13,361 --> 00:35:14,361
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why would you do that?</b></i></font>

848
00:35:14,404 --> 00:35:16,907
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I don't just want you
to set that hearing.</b></i></font>

849
00:35:16,990 --> 00:35:19,618
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want you to bulldoze anyone
who stands in my way.</b></i></font>

850
00:35:20,410 --> 00:35:22,083
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Look, it's up to you.</b></i></font>

851
00:35:22,162 --> 00:35:24,631
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You take the job and the
money and you get me in,</b></i></font>

852
00:35:24,706 --> 00:35:26,083
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>or you stay
on a sinking ship</b></i></font>

853
00:35:26,166 --> 00:35:28,686
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and wait for them to figure out
that you're the one who sank it.</b></i></font>

854
00:35:34,132 --> 00:35:35,634
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'll make it happen.
Yeah.</b></i></font>

855
00:35:35,884 --> 00:35:37,352
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm not surprised.</b></i></font>

856
00:35:44,976 --> 00:35:47,695
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I would have thought you'd
be at happy hour by now.</b></i></font>

857
00:35:47,771 --> 00:35:49,318
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>These days, my happy
hour is the 60 minutes</b></i></font>

858
00:35:49,397 --> 00:35:51,650
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>from the time I get home
to the time I pass out.</b></i></font>

859
00:35:51,733 --> 00:35:52,905
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're a hard worker, Stu.</b></i></font>

860
00:35:52,984 --> 00:35:54,611
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Turns out they don't just give
you money for your looks.</b></i></font>

861
00:35:54,736 --> 00:35:56,738
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hmm. But you didn't come
all the way back here</b></i></font>

862
00:35:56,821 --> 00:35:58,573
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>just to tell me
how hard I work.</b></i></font>

863
00:35:58,865 --> 00:36:00,617
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I came to see
if you'd reconsider.</b></i></font>

864
00:36:01,743 --> 00:36:03,541
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You couldn't beat it, could you?
No.</b></i></font>

865
00:36:03,995 --> 00:36:05,497
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But that's not
why I'm here.</b></i></font>

866
00:36:05,580 --> 00:36:06,672
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Then why are you here?</b></i></font>

867
00:36:06,748 --> 00:36:08,216
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because even though
I didn't like your terms,</b></i></font>

868
00:36:08,291 --> 00:36:11,386
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you spoke to me as an equal and
you treated me with respect.</b></i></font>

869
00:36:11,461 --> 00:36:14,055
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And that's the kind of person I
want to be in business with.</b></i></font>

870
00:36:15,090 --> 00:36:18,845
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What would you say if I told you
the offer was back on the table?</b></i></font>

871
00:36:18,927 --> 00:36:19,927
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'd say my assumption is</b></i></font>

872
00:36:19,969 --> 00:36:22,267
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>the terms won't be as good as
they were the first time around.</b></i></font>

873
00:36:22,347 --> 00:36:23,724
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The terms
aren't going to change.</b></i></font>

874
00:36:23,807 --> 00:36:24,854
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why not?</b></i></font>

875
00:36:25,266 --> 00:36:27,018
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Because I don't want to go
into business with someone</b></i></font>

876
00:36:27,102 --> 00:36:29,446
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>who feels like I'm
giving them the shaft.</b></i></font>

877
00:36:29,521 --> 00:36:32,445
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I want to go into business with someone
who's happy with my partnership.</b></i></font>

878
00:36:34,359 --> 00:36:35,702
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thank you, Stu.</b></i></font>

879
00:36:36,194 --> 00:36:37,821
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're welcome, Donna.</b></i></font>

880
00:36:37,904 --> 00:36:39,702
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Oh, and just so you know,</b></i></font>

881
00:36:39,781 --> 00:36:42,034
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>when I put my money
where my mouth is,</b></i></font>

882
00:36:42,117 --> 00:36:44,370
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I throw everything
I have into it.</b></i></font>

883
00:36:45,704 --> 00:36:49,254
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I wouldn't expect anything less
from a big mouth like you.</b></i></font>

884
00:36:57,966 --> 00:36:59,058
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Done?</b></i></font>

885
00:37:00,135 --> 00:37:01,261
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Done.</b></i></font>

886
00:37:01,970 --> 00:37:03,222
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I've got to say,
the world's going to be</b></i></font>

887
00:37:03,304 --> 00:37:05,056
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>a better place
with you as a lawyer.</b></i></font>

888
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:08,360
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Why? Because we just strong-armed
some jackass into doing what we want?</b></i></font>

889
00:37:08,435 --> 00:37:12,281
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, because you did what it took to
get those miners what they deserve.</b></i></font>

890
00:37:12,355 --> 00:37:14,028
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Speaking of which. You want
to come with me after this?</b></i></font>

891
00:37:14,357 --> 00:37:15,358
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Where you going?</b></i></font>

892
00:37:15,442 --> 00:37:17,035
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>To tell those miners
that the world's best lawyer</b></i></font>

893
00:37:17,110 --> 00:37:18,282
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>just got them
what they deserved.</b></i></font>

894
00:37:18,361 --> 00:37:19,487
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Second best.</b></i></font>

895
00:37:19,571 --> 00:37:21,369
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Ah, potato, potahto.</b></i></font>

896
00:37:24,075 --> 00:37:26,123
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Seriously, Mike,
you go tell them.</b></i></font>

897
00:37:26,202 --> 00:37:27,545
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Besides, after that,</b></i></font>

898
00:37:28,079 --> 00:37:30,548
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>you've got some preparing
to do for that hearing.</b></i></font>

899
00:37:30,957 --> 00:37:32,379
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What are you
talking about?</b></i></font>

900
00:37:32,792 --> 00:37:34,260
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I just told you,
Seidel's got it in the bag.</b></i></font>

901
00:37:34,335 --> 00:37:36,258
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And if you think there isn't
going to be some kind of hitch,</b></i></font>

902
00:37:36,337 --> 00:37:37,384
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I haven't taught you shit.</b></i></font>

903
00:37:37,464 --> 00:37:39,307
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>If you think whatever it is,
I can't handle it,</b></i></font>

904
00:37:39,382 --> 00:37:40,804
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>then you have not
been paying attention.</b></i></font>

905
00:37:40,884 --> 00:37:43,558
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You mean like when you handled
yourself into going to prison?</b></i></font>

906
00:37:43,636 --> 00:37:45,638
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>No, I mean when I came out
smelling like a rose.</b></i></font>

907
00:37:45,722 --> 00:37:47,816
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Hey, I was there
when you came out.</b></i></font>

908
00:37:47,932 --> 00:37:50,606
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And rose wasn't the aroma you
were emanating.</b></i></font>

909
00:37:50,685 --> 00:37:52,733
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You're right,
I was emanating awesome.</b></i></font>

910
00:37:54,147 --> 00:37:56,070
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You really are like me,
aren't you?</b></i></font>

911
00:37:56,149 --> 00:37:57,617
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Unfortunately.</b></i></font>

912
00:37:59,110 --> 00:38:00,703
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Welcome back
to the Bar, Mike.</b></i></font>

913
00:38:00,904 --> 00:38:02,326
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Thanks, Harvey.</b></i></font>

914
00:38:05,408 --> 00:38:09,538
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Technically, I wasn't... Yeah. Actually,
you really weren't in the Bar, ever.</b></i></font>

915
00:38:16,461 --> 00:38:18,509
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'd ask how your day was,</b></i></font>

916
00:38:18,588 --> 00:38:21,683
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>but the last time I did that,
it didn't go very well.</b></i></font>

917
00:38:22,550 --> 00:38:24,894
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara, can I be
honest with you?</b></i></font>

918
00:38:24,969 --> 00:38:26,346
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Of course.</b></i></font>

919
00:38:26,429 --> 00:38:28,147
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You can tell me anything.</b></i></font>

920
00:38:28,223 --> 00:38:30,317
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's part of getting to know each other.
I told you that.</b></i></font>

921
00:38:30,391 --> 00:38:32,814
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I'm just not sure that this
is what you had in mind.</b></i></font>

922
00:38:33,812 --> 00:38:36,361
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Louis, what is going on?</b></i></font>

923
00:38:36,439 --> 00:38:39,488
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>The other day, when I didn't want
to tell you what I was upset about,</b></i></font>

924
00:38:39,567 --> 00:38:44,448
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I was trying to figure out a way
to get Mike Ross into the Bar.</b></i></font>

925
00:38:46,241 --> 00:38:48,494
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You mean the fraud
who worked at your firm?</b></i></font>

926
00:38:48,576 --> 00:38:51,329
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It's a long story. But we're
friends now, and we're past it.</b></i></font>

927
00:38:51,412 --> 00:38:53,164
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you mean,
it's along story?</b></i></font>

928
00:38:55,250 --> 00:38:57,753
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I mean, I knew Mike was a
fraud before he was arrested.</b></i></font>

929
00:38:57,836 --> 00:38:59,213
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I didnât just know.</b></i></font>

930
00:39:01,047 --> 00:39:03,049
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>When I found out about him,</b></i></font>

931
00:39:03,132 --> 00:39:05,681
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>instead of going to the police
or going to the Bar,</b></i></font>

932
00:39:05,760 --> 00:39:08,263
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I leveraged it to get
my name on the wall.</b></i></font>

933
00:39:17,146 --> 00:39:18,614
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara, say something.</b></i></font>

934
00:39:19,023 --> 00:39:20,275
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Say What?</b></i></font>

935
00:39:22,610 --> 00:39:26,365
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You just told me you found out
you were working with a criminal</b></i></font>

936
00:39:26,447 --> 00:39:28,449
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>and you turned it
into a promotion.</b></i></font>

937
00:39:28,533 --> 00:39:29,534
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I know that.</b></i></font>

938
00:39:29,617 --> 00:39:31,369
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But you said that we should
get to know each other.</b></i></font>

939
00:39:31,452 --> 00:39:32,453
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What do you want me
to say, Louis?</b></i></font>

940
00:39:32,537 --> 00:39:35,381
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I didn't know what
your favorite movie was.</b></i></font>

941
00:39:35,456 --> 00:39:36,924
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Or what side
of the bed you like.</b></i></font>

942
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:39,594
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>But I thought at least I knew
what kind of man you were.</b></i></font>

943
00:39:39,669 --> 00:39:41,296
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Tara, please.</b></i></font>

944
00:39:41,754 --> 00:39:44,052
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>This is the thing I'm most
ashamed about in my life.</b></i></font>

945
00:39:44,132 --> 00:39:45,349
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>And I'm telling you
to show you</b></i></font>

946
00:39:45,425 --> 00:39:46,551
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>that I'm never going to hide
anything from you.</b></i></font>

947
00:39:46,634 --> 00:39:49,729
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>Well, maybe you should hide
some things from me.</b></i></font>

948
00:39:49,804 --> 00:39:50,930
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What?</b></i></font>

949
00:39:51,014 --> 00:39:52,357
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>You heard me.</b></i></font>

950
00:39:53,641 --> 00:39:55,063
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>I heard you.</b></i></font>

951
00:39:58,229 --> 00:40:01,654
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>How dare you say that to me after
what I had to find out about you'?</b></i></font>

952
00:40:03,151 --> 00:40:04,778
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>What is that
supposed to mean?</b></i></font>

953
00:40:04,861 --> 00:40:08,661
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>It means you're sitting there like you're
the high priestess of moral authority,</b></i></font>

954
00:40:08,740 --> 00:40:12,370
<font color=#FFFF00><i><b>when the first time we slept
